  "reference_number": "NIC0014",
  "remarks": "\nFidel de Jesus DOMINGUEZ ALVAREZ is the Chief Commissioner of Police in the Department of León. In this position, he is responsible for undermining democracy and the rule of law, repression of civil society and the democratic opposition and human rights violations within the city of León. There are also reasonable grounds to suspect that he is aware of, and has authority over, similar violations committed by his subordinates within the Police Department of León. \n",
